## What This Project Does

* Runs local AI using Ollama
* Fetches stock data using Yahoo Finance
* Fetches news using NewsAPI
* Uses RAG for smarter context
* Displays stock chart in browser

---

## Pro Tips

* Keep Ollama running in background
* Use 8GB+ RAM for better performance
* Never upload .env file to GitHub

